Class SetInitialSpreadReport

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.jasa.report.AbstractAuctionReport
      net.sourceforge.jasa.report.SetInitialSpreadReport
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, net.sourceforge.jabm.event.EventListener, net.sourceforge.jabm.report.Report, net.sourceforge.jabm.util.Parameterizable, net.sourceforge.jabm.util.Resetable, AuctionReport
public class SetInitialSpreadReport
extends AbstractAuctionReport

This class provides a mechanism for initialising the quote prior to actual trading. It allows the initial price of the market to be set without having to simulate a batch auction.

Author:
Steve Phelps
